automate tape_wow
0.26 R:56 0.42:8@smooth 0.3:2 R:14 0.5:10@lin

automate tape_age
0.42 R:24 0.5:0.1@step R:15.9 0.55:0.1@step R:15.9 0.62:0.1@step R:7.9 0.58:0.1@step R:15.9 0.75:9.9@lin

automate noise
0 R:56 0.02:8@smooth 0:2 R:24
